OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773857158
OL,3,CEddie Howe awarded Newcastle's highest
OL,4,Chonour for Carabao Cup win
OL,6,FNewcastle United boss Eddie Howe has
OL,7,Fbeen given the Freedom of Newcastle
OL,8,Fexactly a year after guiding his team
OL,9,Fto the first domestic trophy in 70
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FHe was formally presented with the
OL,13,Fhonour in a small ceremony at the
OL,14,Fclub's training ground amid
OL,15,Fpreparations for the team's trip to
OL,16,FBarcelona for a Champions League game
OL,17,Fon Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
