PN,42502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773857158
OL,3,CEddie Howe awarded Newcastle's highest
OL,4,Chonour for Carabao Cup win
OL,6,FCouncillors agreed to bestow Howe with
OL,7,Fthe honour after he masterminded the
OL,8,Fclub's 2-1 Carabao Cup win over
OL,9,FLiverpool last year.
OL,11,FAround 300,000 people joined a victory
OL,12,Fparade through the city centre when
OL,13,Fthe triumphant players showed off the
OL,14,Ftrophy.
OL,16,FNewcastle City Council leader
OL,17,Fcouncillor Karen Kilgour and the
OL,18,Fcity's Lord Mayor councillor Henry
OL,19,FGallagher presented the honour to Howe
OL,20,Fon Monday (16 March).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
