FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773857158
OL,3,CEddie Howe awarded Newcastle's highest
OL,4,Chonour for Carabao Cup win
OL,6,FHowe said: "It's amazing, it's not
OL,7,Fsomething you ever consider at the
OL,8,Fstart of when you become a football
OL,9,Fmanager.
OL,11,F"I'm very, very grateful for the award
OL,12,Fand the honour.
OL,14,F"Whenever you receive an individual
OL,15,Faccolade it's always a bit
OL,16,Funcomfortable with me because it's
OL,17,Falways about the team, the players,
OL,18,Fthe staff.
OL,26,@nD@LOUsD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773857158
OL,3,CEddie Howe awarded Newcastle's highest
OL,4,Chonour for Carabao Cup win
OL,6,F"I'm just the name at the top, so I
OL,7,Falways feel a slight awkwardness
OL,8,Freceiving it for myself, so I want
OL,9,Feveryone to know I'm receiving it on
OL,10,Fbehalf of everyone at the club.
OL,12,F"The most important thing about what
OL,13,Fmakes this city special is the people.
OL,15,F"The positivity you get, the love for
OL,16,Fthe football club, the love for life,
OL,17,Fthere's always a positive outlook here
OL,18,Fwhich is different to some other
OL,19,Fregions in England.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
