PN,42505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773857158
OL,3,CEddie Howe awarded Newcastle's highest
OL,4,Chonour for Carabao Cup win
OL,6,F"Very funny people, great sense of
OL,7,Fhumour, great to be around, I don't
OL,8,Fthink you ever get bored in the
OL,9,Fcompany of people from Newcastle, so
OL,10,Fit's got that as a fundamental
OL,11,Fstandout.
OL,13,F"The fact that they love their
OL,14,Ffootball club, and that they'd do
OL,15,Fanything for their football club, just
OL,16,Fadds to it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
