PN,42506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773857158
OL,3,CEddie Howe awarded Newcastle's highest
OL,4,Chonour for Carabao Cup win
OL,6,FMs Kilgour, a season-ticket holder and
OL,7,Flifelong fan, said: "Eddie Howe gave
OL,8,Fme one of the best days of my life as
OL,9,Fa Newcastle United fan and season-
OL,10,Fticket holder when Newcastle won the
OL,11,FCarabao Cup, but
OL,13,Fit is the way that he has represented
OL,14,Four club, and our city, on a global
OL,15,Fstage that makes him so special.
OL,17,F"His impact on the club is clear for
OL,18,Fall to see, but it is only Geordies
OL,19,Fhere in Newcastle who can truly
OL,20,Funderstand the impact he had on the
OL,21,Fcity.
OL,26,@oD@UOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
