FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773857158
OL,3,CEddie Howe awarded Newcastle's highest
OL,4,Chonour for Carabao Cup win
OL,6,F"He restored pride in our football
OL,7,Fclub and brought success we had only
OL,8,Fpreviously dreamt of."
OL,10,FThe honorary freeman status is the
OL,11,Fhighest honour the council can bestow
OL,12,Fand Howe joins the likes of Nelson
OL,13,FMandela, Bob Geldof and the late
OL,14,Fcardinal Basil Hume.
OL,16,FThe names of all honorary freemen are
OL,17,Fcarved into the walls of the
OL,18,Fbanqueting hall in the civic centre.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@VO]
