OL,3,CEddie Howe awarded Newcastle's highest
OL,4,Chonour for Carabao Cup win
OL,6,FThe club itself has that honour, as
OL,7,Fwell as other Newcastle United greats
OL,8,FJackie Milburn, Sir Bobby Robson and
OL,9,FAlan Shearer.
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
